          <li class="cs-item">
            <span class="cs-item-number">03</span>
            <div class="cs-item-wrapper">
              <h3 class="cs-h3">People Experiencing Stress or Anxiety</h3>
              <p class="cs-item-text">
                Massage provides a calm, restorative reset that helps lower
                stress levels, settle the nervous system, and promote better
                sleep.
              </p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="cs-item">
            <span class="cs-item-number">04</span>
            <div class="cs-item-wrapper">
              <h3 class="cs-h3">Anyone Seeking Relaxation and Self‑Care</h3>
              <p class="cs-item-text">
                A rejuvenating way to prioritize well‑being—feel lighter, more
                balanced, and ready for the rest of your day.
              </p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <!---SVG Graphic-->
      <img
        class="cs-floater"
        src="https://csimg.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/Images/Graphics/diagnol-ovals.svg"
        alt="graphic"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
        height="710"
        aria-hidden="true"
        width="690"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================ -->
  <!--                   Steps                      -->
  <!-- ============================================ -->

  <section id="steps-1675">
    <div class="cs-container">
      <div class="cs-content">
        <span class="cs-topper">Steps to Book Your Massage</span>
        <h2 class="cs-title">How to Book an Appointment</h2>
        <p class="cs-text">
          Booking a therapeutic massage at Kabayan Healing Touch Massage is
          simple. Follow these steps to reserve your in‑clinic session.
        </p>
      </div>
      <ul class="cs-card-group">
        <li class="cs-item">
          <span class="cs-number">01</span>
          <h3 class="cs-h3">Choose Your Service</h3>
          <p class="cs-item-text">
            Select from our therapeutic treatments: deep‑tissue, hot stone,
            Swedish, cupping, or lymphatic massage—delivered in‑clinic.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="cs-item">
          <span class="cs-number">02</span>
          <h3 class="cs-h3">Pick Your Time</h3>
