          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="cs-item">
          <span class="cs-number">03</span>
          <h3 class="cs-h3">Schedule Your Appointment</h3>
          <p class="cs-item-text">
            Prefer to speak with us? Call or message and we’ll help you secure
            your preferred date and time.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="cs-item">
          <span class="cs-number">04</span>
          <h3 class="cs-h3">Confirm & Relax</h3>
          <p class="cs-item-text">
            Arrive a few minutes early, settle in, and enjoy your
            session—focused, restorative care tailored to your goals.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

